b_battle_solomons23.jpg" border='0' alt='Cruiser USS Phoenix firing her 6-inch guns during the invasion of Cape Gloucester, New Britain, Bismarck Archipelago, circa 24-26 Dec 1943; note photo was taken from fantail, looking forward'></a></td><td><a href='/photo.php?source=all&color=all&list=search&foreigntype=S&foreigntype_id=396'><img src="/images/imagemagick/tmb_person_kinkaid7.jpg" border='0' alt='Vice Admiral Thomas Kinkaid, General Douglas MacArthur, and Colonel Lloyd Labrbas aboard cruiser Phoenix during bombardment of Los Negros Island, 28 Feb 1944; note 40-mm gun mount in background'></a></td></tr></table><a href='/photo.php?source=all&color=all&list=search&foreigntype=S&foreigntype_id=396'>See all 12 photographs of Light Cruiser USS Phoenix</a><br /><br /><br /><br />
